storyInfo: In the abandoned bar, wine and words mix, and people speak uninhibited. Someone from Laterano named Suffering(?) comes to take Mostima away. Sunset approaches, bringing another brawl with it.

attributes.content: 3:21 A.M. \ Clear
Downtown Lungmen, 'The Ends of the Earth' lounge, ruins
Cheers!!
attributes.name: Penguin Logistics

attributes.content: Cheers!!
attributes.name: Penguin Logistics

attributes.content: Whew, tonight sure was a good time.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: You wouldn't think it from the stinkin' pile of garbage we're sittin' in, but it was great. Just thinkin' about somebody else footin' the bill for all our expenses makes me all warm inside!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Texas, if you figured it out earlier, you should have told us.
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: I just guessed.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: You're a really bad liar, you know that...?
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: The boss had it all planned out, didn't he? Don't sweat it~ Eating, drinking, and fighting are good for the body and good for the soul.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: What's wrong? You're not going to join them?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: No, I'm okay.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: I just, how can I say this? I just feel like I can't accept it.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: You get used to it.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: If I'm used to it then it's all over.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Like what was everything tonight even for? And Emperor, he...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: ...gave his life to make the party more fun.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Mostima, you told me you would be giving me a grade for my performance at Penguin Logistics, didn't you?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: I did. I've been thinking about it. And while you didn't exactly mesh with everybody, you made some great strides. That much is clear. Maybe...
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: No.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: I'm not staying here.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Oh? I thought with everything that happened, you'd need Penguin Logistics to be a springboard for you to bigger and better things.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: That was the original idea. Turns out you had that all figured out...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: It's not that I think Penguin Logistics is terrible. Well, it is terrible.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: But I think, with Messengers like this, who live like this...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Even though my common sense tells me it's ridiculously dangerous...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: I think it might be... what I actually want.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Or maybe it's like I'll start to question reality if I don't look at it this way.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: ...like one, completely insane dream.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Yeah. Fistfights, explosions, and high altitude drops will do that to you.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Getting thrown into the deep end with Penguin Logistics isn't great for your mental health.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: But if you've made your decision, and as your fellow Messenger, I wish you luck.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: ...Thanks.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Especially since it means your father won't have any grounds to dock my pay.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: D- dad! I totally forgot about that. I need to talk to him. But what is he even doing right now...?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Mostima! Drink up!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Cheers.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: What's with you suddenly flitting over here? You spilled all over yourself.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: If I take my eyes off you for one second, you could vanish. And I got a lottttt of questions to ask you.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: A lot, huh...? Like about that incident back in Laterano?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: With your sister? Or maybe... my horns?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Hahaha, you're dumbstruck? Oh, Exusiai, you never change. You're always so easy to read.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: MOS! TI! MA!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: All right, all right. I'll tell you.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: ...But right not now. You've been digging into it on your own for a while now, so you must understand.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Um, I don't know why, but it's classified as a state secret now. Does that matter?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: I have to get closure on everything about you.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: You really do, huh...?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: It could be a long and treacherous path, with your precious guns confiscated, the wicked watching you, hounding you to the mouth of hell?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Hm, that's weirdly specific.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: But no big deal. I run pretty fast. They'll never catch me!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Fine.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: You give up?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: I give up. Not that anyone could ever tell you what to do.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: That's not true. There's the boss. And Texas, I'll listen to Texas. Sometimes. Kinda.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Ya hear what they're whisperin' about?
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: I think I heard most of the story already, but to tell the truth, I'm all kinds of curious right now.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: What kinda place is Laterano anyway?
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: ...Don't go digging too deep. It's her choice.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: But what about Bison?
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: He lost his temper quite a few times tonight. He'll get used to it.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: He's an excellent new-comer to this industry. Is it okay to leave him like that?
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Bison~ Lemme give ya a copy of the Great Foodie Guide. I did it up myself after real, in-person, on-site investigations!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: You wrote the Foodie Guide!
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Hehe. Advertisin's a real important revenue stream!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: ...Wow. Okay, you'll have to give me some secret recommendations.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: By the way, there's some fancy rich guy butler-looking dude standing outside the door?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Can ya really say he's outside the door when the walls are crumbled like so? *Sigh* And we have to pay the retainage for the small thruster this month...
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: ...I'm going to get some air.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Young Master.
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: I know everything.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Father and Emperor had a deal at the same time a Siracusan gang came up against the Rat King, is that right?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Everything has a purpose, Young Master. You performed spectacularly well, given the circumstances. The Master of the House is most pleased.
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: And yet, I...
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: Twice. That's how many times you followed my dad's order and did the trick with my shield.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Thank you... Young Master.
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: *Sigh* Having been through so much, how can we still relax and enjoy a party over broken glass and splintered barstools?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: This kind of boundless optimism is born from the innumerable life-or-death experiences of a life well lived, Young Master.
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: I know. But they're Messengers. Why do they always risk their lives?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: That's what a Messenger does. Should you leave home, leave the Master of the House, and leave Lungmen, you too will come to understand.
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: ...I hope so.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Shall we head back and see the Master of the House?
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: Father's probably plotting something with Chief Wei right now. I'm sure it's something very important that I can't concern myself with.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: You are very clever, but the Master of the House did not make these choices to be rid of you. You will grow stronger, and more tenacious.
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: ...Maybe. I'm not sure if I really will see that day.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: You go to my father. I need to... cut loose a bit.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: I understand. Do enjoy yourself, Young Master.
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: Oh, there was one more thing.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Butler

attributes.content: I did have a very good time tonight.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: ...Nnng...
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: She gets drunk and makes trouble.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: But she sure is cute when she's quiet, isn't she? A little sister to be proud of.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: I don't care about her or her sister, but you need to stop her from digging any deeper into that stuff. We don't need that trouble.
Not to mention, the most important thing...
Weren't you just telling me not to talk in such a roundabout way?
What do you mean? Isn't it scarier how you can apparently hear everything I say all the time? Did you bug the place or something?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: You should always remember who made me your keeper.
...Okay then, Miss 'Keeper,' what are you calling yourself these days?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Why do you ask?
It's time for your routine report, isn't it? I've been waiting all night. The big shots up top don't have any new ideas?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Why should I tell you?
I have a right to know. We're colleagues, aren't we?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: And I'm personally very interested in the way you change your duties each month.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Fine. I guess we would need codenames to refer to each other in case something happens.
I'm under the Notarial Hall this time. The usual. Independent special operations. Duty name... it's...
What's the name?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: ...Suffering.
Um. What? Why?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: How should I know! They said they watched some slasher flick and then decided they were going to change it to this with no explanation...
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Suffering? All right. At least it's less cringey than last time's 'Chosen Overseer.'
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Hmph. They're taking the piss out of someone else's job, and why did the Notarial Hall agree to it?
attributes.name: Chosen Overseer?

attributes.content: Did they think for even a moment, what if I had to meet Wei Yenwu? How am I supposed to announce myself?!
attributes.name: Chosen Overseer?

attributes.content: 'Hello. I'm Suffering from the Laterano Notarial Hall. It's a pleasure to meet you.'
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Was 'Tomb Knight' better? Or 'Super Sticky' from last month? Or 'Treasure Guardian' that came earlier than them?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: When you first volunteered to go with me, I really thought Laterano had an organization called the Treasure Guardians, you know...?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: That's enough!
attributes.name: Treasure Guardian?

attributes.content: ...I'm writing a letter to Laterano right now. If they don't give me a perfectly ordinary assignment, they better not expect to get regular correspondences from me anymore.
attributes.name: Treasure Guardian?

attributes.content: You need to understand where they're coming from. It's not easy to trust a horned Sankta.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Can't they just give me a normal assignment?!
attributes.name: Treasure Guardian?

attributes.content: An exceptional promotion would be cause for suspicion. And being so frantic all the time will give you wrinkles, Miss Suffering.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Woah, don't take it so seriously. Drawing your gun at the first disagreement is a pretty bad habit.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Whatever. Watching your performance all night made me sick. You're such a ham.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Then is it about time we leave Lungmen? I could take you shopping, as a way of making it up to you.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: ...Yeah, that's a good idea.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Which reminds me, you must've made a lot of money this time around? How about sending some my way? A little hospitality?
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: We're both from Laterano. Who's the host here?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Fine. By the way, this angel's halo is blindingly bright.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: They get in the way sometimes.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Lucky you don't have that problem, fallen angel.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Are you jealous? I could buy you a fluorescent lamp to wear on your head.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Sounds like a pain. How do you deal with it?
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Instinct. The moment we start using language, the halo appears.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Like the first time you blurt out 'mama' or 'dada?' What a beautiful image.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Haha. Exusiai's first word was 'sis.' Even though they're not blood related, they still...
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Enough. Let's not talk about her sister. Even if Laterano doesn't care, it's not a topic for casual conversation.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: It's because you leveled this precious gun at the captain that you fell.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Do you really plan to tell her the whole story someday? The little sister of your beloved battle-sister?
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Hm... You've followed me this long and I still haven't told you. It might be that you, also my 'beloved battle-sister...' have a really bad temper?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: I'm only under obligation to remind you that you must not speak even one word of what happened at Kazdel.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: But what about my travel memoir?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Sounds great. Hey, why don't you go get your staff back from that freaky guy before I write you up for it.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: You're running out of time.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Yep. You're right. I'll do exactly as Suffering says.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: You...
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: ...Boss, is there more work to do?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Before you leave Lungmen, I'll have a real pain in the ass job for you, no doubt.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Wait, you're not dead...? How much did you hear?
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: A gentleman don't eavesdrop on two ladies havin' a private conversation.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Plus I don't need to. Bein' omniscient and all.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: ...so you heard everything.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Whatever. You're Emperor. It's fine.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Did you really feel like you wanted to kill him back there...? I guess that's our Suffering...
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Shove it. Don't talk about me like I'm some kind of villain.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Would you ever consider joining Penguin Logistics? You wouldn't have to keep swapping around these cringey codenames.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: ...I must keep track of you, as a Laterano.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Right. It's just an idea I had. It's hard not to use your real name, you know.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Aight, time for you to bounce. This ain't a Laterano cathedral. We don't welcome Suffering here.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: I... whatever.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: I'm going to go... send a letter.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: ...Damn it.
attributes.name: Suffering?

attributes.content: Uh huh. Every one of them reports gets some government office swappin' your name around, huh? Seems like you're real popular over there.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: I think at least half the reason they do it is just because it's fun for them.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: It's fun, huh? Mmm, makes sense. Sounds like at least a couple Laterano big shots know how to live.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: ...Hold up. Fun... someplace fun...
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Aight, I got a idea. Mostima, you're gonna like this job. You know what? This job's gonna blow you away. You just wait 'til I hit you up.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: It really worries me when you talk like that, boss... But the sun's almost up. I better go find her.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Since everything here's all wrapped up with a nice little bow, it's time for me to leave. Say goodbye to everyone for me.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Especially Exusiai. And buy her dinner for me.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Don't worry about it.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: We all gonna see each other again real soon.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: ...Wow... the sun's coming up.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: How do I get back? Uh oh... I think I'm lost...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Oh, I'm here. How do I always end up coming back here?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Is that...?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Mostima? Oh, she's praying. I better not bother her...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: I wanna see the sunrise!
attributes.name: Passerby

attributes.content: Sorry, he's drunk. Can you let us by? Thanks!
attributes.name: Passerby

attributes.content: Erm... Okay...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Damn! Mostima... she's already gone.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: (But it looked like there was some kind of red shadow next to her? Did I see that right?)
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Hey, that kid over there's in the way.
attributes.name: Punk

attributes.content: Me?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: You're the prince of MDL, aren't you? The rich as hell prince!
attributes.name: Punk

attributes.content: Why don't you come with us? Just need a minute of your time.
attributes.name: Punk

attributes.content: ...Again?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: ...Um, heh heh, well...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: What are you laughing at?
attributes.name: Punk

attributes.content: Hey! The little punk wants to fight! Let's get him, boys!
attributes.name: Punk

attributes.content: Speed of Light / DJ OKAWARI
——Special Thanks——
Candy catering — Victoria Rainbow Sweets
Major expenditures on stupid things — Mountain Dash Logistics
Getting beaten for no reason — Tung's Finballs
Extra — Suffering from Laterano...?
Possibly being dead — The Gambino Family
Guest appearance while taking a walk — 'Rat King' of the Lungmen Slums
And the glorious, the incredible, the unstoppable,
who clear any obstacle, solve any case, complete any job,
Penguin Logistics
This new car is great.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Yeah! Let's go to the docks and seek revenge for Bison!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Texas, can ya take it a little slower, I'm puttin' some cream on Bison...
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Ah! Sorry!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: What's to be sorry for? He got a bloody nose. Just cram the cream up there.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: ...It's okay. I'll do it.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Yeah, that's about right for the son of that dumbass cow. Can't give anybody an inch.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: We got three hours and twenty-five minutes until we gotta see off Bison. That's more than enough time for a farewell party.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Let's see how many punks come at us.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Sorry, I didn't mean to be a bother...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Bother? Nah. No bother.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Honestly, I been watchin' these wannabes for a while. They don't even know how to do crime.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Those clowns tryin' to share a city with us? That's a crime.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: That makes us sound like we're the most dangerous?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Just up ahead! That warehouse is their hideout!
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Grab whatever you want. Texas, crash us on in there!
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: On it!
attributes.name: Texas
